WEBVTT

00:00:03.128 --> 00:00:06.416
Shah Rukh Khan: World famous education
scientist Sugata Mitra believes

00:00:06.416 --> 00:00:10.940
that our kids can not only learn well,
they can also teach well.

00:00:11.140 --> 00:00:12.710
Teachers may or may not be there, 


00:00:12.710 --> 00:00:15.030
they will surely be able 
to teach each other.

00:00:15.030 --> 00:00:18.050
Today, he has traveled from UK to India

00:00:18.050 --> 00:00:20.520
just to speak with us -- Sugata Mitra.

00:00:20.520 --> 00:00:23.030
The education scientist 
who has successfully changed


00:00:23.030 --> 00:00:25.750
the syllabus of teaching 
and learning across the globe.

00:00:25.750 --> 00:00:28.700
Please welcome on stage, Mr. Sugata Mitra.

00:00:28.700 --> 00:00:34.800
(Applause)